Adult = 1	RFID tag
Time: current	continuous	Date time	0-24hrs	Real-time clock
Time: feeding schedule
	discrete	Boolean	08:00AM
18:00PM	clock
Portion quantity 	discrete	Boolean	200 or 500 grams	Scale sensor
food level of container
	discrete	Boolean	True=1 
False= 0	sensor
